{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/blog/tera-saturday-6-hide-and-sheep","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><em>Welcome to the return of TeraSaturday, a not-so-weekly update post about all the neat stuff that has been going on in\nthe world of Terasology! Half blog, half changelog, completely cool.</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"-since-last-terasaturday-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-since-last-terasaturday-\" aria-label=\" since last terasaturday  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ğŸ“° Since last TeraSaturday ...</h2>\n<p>We had the <strong>November Play Test</strong> last Sunday, trying out all the new and exciting things that have been added over the last months. We all tested the first release candidate for the upcoming stable version to identify weak spots we want to smooth out. You can download <a href=\"https://github.com/MovingBlocks/Terasology/releases/tag/v4.1.0-rc.1\">Engine 4.1.0 / Alpha 17 Preview (Release Candidate 1)</a> as <strong>Terasology (Nightly) #1119</strong> in the launcher. <em>@Skaldarnar</em> streamed via <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/terasology\">twitch</a>, you can watch the (slightly trimmed) recording below - as always, feedback is welcome ğŸ¤“</p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QbD8Z98Evb4\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n<p>We would like to say a warm \"welcome ğŸ‘‹\" to <em>@HajdaM</em> and warm \"welcome back ğŸ‘‹\" to <em>@iHDeveloper</em> who both jumped straight from play-testing into coding, e.g., by improving performance or the integration with Discord. <em>@Michael P</em> and <em>@Niruandaleth</em> are still crawling through the JOML conversion ğŸ‘©â€ğŸ« and <em>@DarkWeird</em>, among other things, disassembles our engine into smaller subsystems ğŸ‘¨â€ğŸ”§</p>\n<p>Overall, we again merged more than <strong>60 PRs</strong> on <a href=\"https://github.com/search?q=org%3AMovingBlocks+type%3Apr+merged%3A2020-11-20..2020-11-28\">the engine</a> and in <a href=\"https://github.com/search?q=org%3ATerasology+type%3Apr+merged%3A2020-11-20..2020-11-28\">module space</a> over the last week, with more contributions from <em>@4D enthusiast</em> and <em>@Cervator</em>. ğŸ’ª</p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; left:0; width: 100%;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 26.5625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/ModuleSite/static/784ac69d903fe05d52d8364561ee81d3/3e828/discord-integration.webp 192w,\n/ModuleSite/static/784ac69d903fe05d52d8364561ee81d3/e6f2f/discord-integration.webp 384w,\n/ModuleSite/static/784ac69d903fe05d52d8364561ee81d3/e88ff/discord-integration.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/ModuleSite/static/784ac69d903fe05d52d8364561ee81d3/7809d/discord-integration.jpg 192w,\n/ModuleSite/static/784ac69d903fe05d52d8364561ee81d3/4ecad/discord-integration.jpg 384w,\n/ModuleSite/static/784ac69d903fe05d52d8364561ee81d3/b4294/discord-integration.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" type=\"image/jpeg\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/ModuleSite/static/784ac69d903fe05d52d8364561ee81d3/b4294/discord-integration.jpg\" alt=\"Discord Integration\" title=\"Discord Integration\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"-bug-fixes-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-bug-fixes-\" aria-label=\" bug fixes  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ğŸ› Bug Fixes ğŸ</h2>\n<p>ğŸ•¹ You may enjoy this play-test video by <em>Lowricsec</em> who gave our May release a try. This has slipped our attention for 3 months, but here you go ğŸ® Videos like these are a great source of both inspiration and new bugs to fix. It helps us to identify the issues that really affect the player, and we often also get some suggestions on how this might be fixed.</p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/R3CozWpC3G0\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n<p><em>@Niruandaleth</em> and <em>@Skaldarnar</em> took this as an opportunity to address some of those bugs. They tweaked the brightness at night, adjusted the player height and model scale, pushed the name tags back into place, and got rid of some bugs which crashed the game. Health regeneration was also fixed, so no more blocks regaining their health faster than you can hit 'em. <em>@DarkWeird</em> also contributed here, investigating some networking issues to make the \"Join Game\" work smoothly again.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; left:0; width: 100%;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/3e828/night-brightness.webp 192w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/e6f2f/night-brightness.webp 384w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/8b983/night-brightness.webp 768w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/b2d4b/night-brightness.webp 1152w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/0abaa/night-brightness.webp 1536w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/919bf/night-brightness.webp 3200w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/8514f/night-brightness.png 192w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/804b2/night-brightness.png 384w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/e5715/night-brightness.png 768w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/4ad3a/night-brightness.png 1152w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/71c1d/night-brightness.png 1536w,\n/ModuleSite/static/4ba418aa1caef09394fd7e5a8ad77ed4/dcef9/night-brightness.png 3200w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n      